title: 102: True or False: Prospect Edition
itunes:title: 102: True or False: Prospect Edition
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the latest rumors surrounding the 2016 NFL draft, including why Christian Hackenberg is the perfect fit for the Cowboys.  The guys then play a little game of true or false as they debate where a number of big-name prospects will land on draft day.
